# CODEOWNERS — review routing for talos-platform-base
#
# Order matters: later patterns override earlier ones.
# Syntax: https://docs.github.com/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# Default: repo owner reviews everything.
*                                                @nosmoht

# Hard-constraint surfaces — require explicit owner review.
/AGENTS.md                                       @nosmoht
/CLAUDE.md                                       @nosmoht
/SECURITY.md                                     @nosmoht
/CODEOWNERS                                      @nosmoht
/MAINTAINERS.md                                  @nosmoht

# ADRs — decision-grade documents.
/docs/adr-*.md                                   @nosmoht

# PNI subsystem — capability-first contract.
/kubernetes/base/infrastructure/platform-network-interface/  @nosmoht
/docs/capability-architecture.md                 @nosmoht
/docs/capability-reference.md                    @nosmoht
/docs/pni-cookbook.md                            @nosmoht

# OCI publish surface — supply-chain critical.
/.github/workflows/oci-publish.yml               @nosmoht
/docs/oci-artifact-verification.md               @nosmoht

# Talos machine-config patches — boot-loop risk.
/talos/                                          @nosmoht
